<div id="outline-container-orge51f5fb" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orge51f5fb"><span class="section-number-3">7.2</span> The Files We Build</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-7-2">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>vmlinuz</li>
<li>initrd</li>
<li>modules, in the hundreds</li>
</ol>
